sentences: Quincy Delight Jones III (born 23 December 1968), better known as QDIII, QD3 and Snoopy, is a Swedish-American music producer and film producer.
Jones is also a hip hop DJ; he released an album called Soundlab (1991).
Jones is known for his documentary The Carter (2009), about rapper Lil Wayne.
In 2011, Jones co-founded the health and wellness lifestyle company Feel Rich, Inc. with partner Shawn Ullman, which aimed at promoting "health as the new wealth" to urban communities.
